===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|informacion}}, {{m|enm|enformacion}}, borrowed from {{bor|en|xno|informacioun}}, {{m|en|enformation}}, {{bor|en|fro|information}}, from {{der|en|la|īnfōrmātiō||formation, conception; education}}, from the participle stem of {{m|la|īnformāre||to inform}}. Compare {{cog|fy|ynformaasje||information}}, Dutch {{m|nl|informatie||information}}, German {{m|de|Information||information}}, Danish {{m|da|information||information}}, Swedish {{m|sv|information||information}}.

